here to run this project in your local 
1. Download the zip folder and unzip it
2. Add the folder to the VS code or any other editor
3. Then open the terminal and run it using nodemon command to run the app.js
    * nodemon app
4. Then it will be running in the localhost 3000 port
5. Go check it in a browser by adding the address
    * http://localhost:3000/

6. And VOILA you got it
        
